build2: build2 is a cross-platform build toolchain for C/C++.  
build2:  
build2: build2 is a hierarchy of tools consisting of a general-purpose build 
build2: system, package manager, and project manager. It is primarily aimed at 
build2: C/C++ projects as well as mixed-language projects.  
